WEBVTT

00:03:00.061 --> 00:03:01.951
7:08pm.

00:03:02.580 --> 00:03:05.549
I sat in seat 7A.

00:03:06.009 --> 00:03:07.352
Fly Emirates.

00:03:09.427 --> 00:03:13.105
One of the most gorgeous,
beautiful women I've ever seen walked up,

00:03:14.246 --> 00:03:17.052
red little hat with a white veil.

00:03:17.792 --> 00:03:20.725
I'm looking terrified,
I have no idea what I'm doing.

00:03:21.391 --> 00:03:23.617
She hands me this warm towel --

00:03:23.641 --> 00:03:25.722
warm, steamy, snow white.

00:03:27.686 --> 00:03:30.000
I'm looking at this warm towel;